name: Galactic Dogfight
overview: Published as a game of the notorious "Cassette 50" collection. This is a head-to-head, 2 player game where you try to shot down your opponent's five planes using rockets or Air-Mines. Turbo boosts can also be used to get yourself out of trouble or to surprise your opponent. You have 5 mines and 5 turbo boosts to last you for 5 dogfights, so you them with care.
